# Requirements

1. Add a role column to the users table. Set the default value to user.

2. Add a manage users inteface to the Todo App
    - allow admin to add / update / delete user
    - allow admin to change user's password
    - manage users page can only be accessed by admin

3. Convert all the functionality of the manage users to OOP

4. Convert all the functionality of tasks to OOP

5. Convert all the functionality of authentication to OOP